data.description: Looking for Space?  This home has BEAUTIFUL UPDATES and SO MUCH SPACE! Plenty of room to entertain in the updated kitchen a beaufitul island, and a large custom built pantry with soft close drawers.  Huge primary bedroom with sitting area and fabulous 12x12 walk-in closet.  Spacious hallway loft, and all 3 generous bedrooms have new carpeting and walk in closets.  Enjoy your new fenced in backyard with a 850 sq ft concrete patio with a built in fire pit.   This home has been meticulously maintained and updated with new paint, carpeting, flooring, doors, updated bathrooms, and kitchen.  Need even more space? Full unfinished basement with a clean slate for your design.  Everything has been updated, nothing to do but move in and start making memories!
